===Background===
A member of House Fossoway fought in the [[Trial by seven of Duncan the Tall]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Justice of the Seven Kingdoms]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 2]]===
House Fossoway follows their liege lords, House Tyrell, in pledging support to [[Renly Baratheon]]'s claim to the [[Iron Throne]]. Following the [[Assassination of Renly I|death]] of Renly, however, the Fossoways do not follow their Tyrell overlords and instead go over to [[Stannis Baratheon|Stannis]]. They participate in the [[Battle of the Blackwater]].&lt;ref&gt;Season 2 Bluray: War of the Five Kings feature&lt;/ref&gt;
